{"tid":1604194,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[寵物online] 操蟲師戰術討論","createTime":"2019-09-30T01:38:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T09:52:20.000Z","uid":71428,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"a3e39ba771c0bdd5ca06c831cd9f845766fcef60","tid":1604194,"uid":71428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T01:38:54.000Z","msg":"遊戲介紹: 玩家可將各種昆蟲兵種放入精靈球, 並向目標建築物 (如:狗屋) 進擊攻擊, 能有效影響敵人休息, 並減少圍攻目標需時和兵力減少<br />\n<br />\n兵種:<br />\n蟲系被動技: 大量繁殖, 難以消滅<br />\n<br />\n白蟻/飛蟻 (地面/飛行系)<br />\n對木屬性建築物造成持續傷害<br />\n入手難度: 3/5<br />\n<br />\n曱甴 (地面/飛行系)<br />\n對糧食使用塗毒技能. 對敵人使用精神攻擊<br />\n入手難度: 因應玩家勇氣值以定<br />\n<br />\n蟋蟀(地面系) <br />\n對敵人使用精神攻擊<br />\n入手難度: 1/5<br />\n<br />\n草蜢(地面/飛行系):<br />\n對敵人使用精神攻擊<br />\n入手難度: 1/5<br />\n<br />\n蝨(地面系)<br />\n對敵人附加DEBUFF效果<br />\n入手難度: 5/5<br />\n<br />\n公測日期: coming soon<br />\n歡迎提供兵種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5edbc138f6149bc6111634e0fc36db99c3557f3b","tid":1604194,"uid":219583,"like":1,"dislike":25,"score":-24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T01:40:34.000Z","msg":"屌你老母教人玩生命?"},{"pid":"a38539c9b9d752885f89f7e6349fb75c7d61f40d","tid":1604194,"uid":71428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T01:40:34.000Z","msg":"自推十連擊"},{"pid":"205a56ca346a55ad471c3935d85a192bfa1c4bf6","tid":1604194,"uid":71428,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5edbc138f6149bc6111634e0fc36db99c3557f3b","tid":1604194,"uid":219583,"like":1,"dislike":25,"score":-24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T01:40:34.000Z","msg":"屌你老母教人玩生命?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T01:41:26.000Z","msg":"你唔打機架?"},{"pid":"2a415a77dc4fc18b2546dcdcf53d330d794cba03","tid":1604194,"uid":71428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T01:41:37.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"183bbc444407c8cfc5aaa4d9aa10c8d6aeada3f5","tid":1604194,"uid":219583,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"205a56ca346a55ad471c3935d85a192bfa1c4bf6","tid":1604194,"uid